7.40	David_Klass	David Klass	David Klass is an American screenwriter and novelist. He has written more than 40 screenplays for Hollywood studios and published 14 young adult novels. His screenplays are primarily character-based thrillers for adults, while his novels often tell the stories of teenagers in crisis.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/DavidKlass.JPG/220px-DavidKlass.JPG
